      "content": "it's just gonna be a huge difference though. i was worried about it. our current work with the grit and the moral ambiguity is what makes the books sell, you know? if we move to this \"standard\" template, it's basically gonna feel like generic, watered-down stuff. i'm worried the readers aren't gonna care as much if the characters aren't real anymore. u think it's actually possible to keep the magic alive with these new constraints?",
